  • Reference

    UNDP minimal dataset

    pnud_min.Rd

    A dataset that contains UNDP information for municipalities by years.

    pnud_min

    Format

    a data frame with 16686 rows and 15 columns.

    pnud_siglas

    Source

    https://www.br.undp.org/content/brazil/pt/home/idh0/atlas-do-desenvolvimento-humano/atlas-dos-municipios.html
